<view>
  <view class='title'>完成以下6步，就可以解锁附近的WiFi了</view>
  <view class='row-style'>
    <text>1.点击左上角“设置”返回设置列表</text>
  </view>
  <view class='row-style'>
    <text>2.从设置列表顶部进入“无线局域网”</text>
  </view>
  <view class='row-style'>
    <text>3.如果未打开WiFi开关，请打开</text>
  </view>
  <view class='row-style'>
    <text>4.如果已打开WiFi开关，请关闭并重开</text>
  </view>
  <view class='row-style'>
    <text>5.等待WiFi列表刷新</text>
  </view>
  <view class='row-style'>
    <text>6.返回小程序，点击连接</text>
  </view>
  <button class='connect-button' bindtap="getWifiList">看懂了，去连接</button>
</view>